---

<section
    class="section-characters relative py-32 md:py-52 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-visible bg-transparent"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[-1] bg-[#121212]"></div>

    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
        <div
            class="absolute top-[10%] left-[-10%] w-[70%] h-[90%] bg-[#999999]/60 blur-[150px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen"
        >
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-10%] w-[60%] h-[80%] bg-[#CB6859]/20 blur-[140px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen opacity-60"
        >
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0D0D0D] via-transparent to-[#0D0D0D] opacity-90"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[1800px] mx-auto relative z-20 flex flex-col gap-24">
        <div
            class="w-full text-center space-y-8 translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
        >
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <span
                    class="text-[#D9895B] text-[10px] font-cinzel font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em]"
                    >Identidad Única</span
                >
                <div
                    class="h-[1px] w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#D9895B] to-transparent"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2
                class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-cinzel font-bold leading-none text-[#F2E6D8] tracking-tighter"
            >
                Forja tu <br />
                <span
                    class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D9895B] via-[#CB6859] to-[#BF5E5E]"
                >
                    Legado
                </span>
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start"
        >
            <div
                class="flex flex-col gap-10 items-center text-center relative group translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[#5B5E67]/20 blur-[80px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="relative w-full p-2 border-2 border-double border-[#5B5E67]/40 bg-[#0D0D0D]/50 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-700 group-hover:border-[#D9895B]/60"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute -top-1 -left-1 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#D9895B]"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#D9895B]"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
                        <img
                            src="/GreedFall/Screen_4.png"
                            alt="Nuevos Entornos GreedFall"
                            class="w-full h-auto object-cover transition-transform duration-[2000ms] group-hover:scale-105 opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p
                    class="font-serif italic text-sm md:text-xl text-[#F2E6D8]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-lg px-4"
                >
                    Numerosas referencias al primer juego, al tiempo que
                    introduce nuevos personajes y entornos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col gap-10 items-center text-center relative group translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[#BF5E5E]/20 blur-[80px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="relative w-full p-2 border-2 border-double border-[#BF5E5E]/40 bg-[#0D0D0D]/50 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-700 group-hover:border-[#CB6859]/60"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#CB6859]"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute -bottom-1 -left-1 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#CB6859]"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
                        <img
                            src="/GreedFall/Screen_3.png"
                            alt="Personalización de Personaje"
                            class="w-full h-auto object-cover transition-transform duration-[2000ms] group-hover:scale-105 opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p
                    class="font-serif italic text-sm md:text-xl text-[#F2E6D8]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-lg px-4"
                >
                    Personajes con identidades fuertes, cuya apariencia, equipo
                    y habilidades puedes personalizar
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section-characters {
        contain: paint;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(
            to bottom,
            transparent,
            black 15%,
            black 85%,
            transparent
        );
    }
</style>
